Package: y-ppa-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, yad (>= 0.24.1), libnotify-bin, ppa-purge, python3-software-properties, wget, xterm, launchpad-getkeys (>= 0.3.2), python, python-launchpadlib, python-appindicator, python-gtk2, python-apt, python-vte, xclip, policykit-1
Recommends: gksu | kdesudo
Description: Y PPA Manager
 .
 Easily manage PPAs: add, remove, purge and search in 
 all Launchpad PPAs using a graphical interface. The 
 search feature allows you to add the found PPAs, list
 the packages and their versions in a PPA or download 
 some packages in the PPA.
